->fs tech
@node tech "technical information
How to find out which mode should be used:

Usually you should use word mode, as it is ok for the most games,
but there are some exceptions:

- If the game uses very big numbers, higher than 65535, you should
  try long mode.

- If you want to manipulate very small numbers (1-255) AND WORD
  MODE DIDN'T SUCCEED, try byte mode as it is very slow due to
  some technical reasons. (Not a problem caused be Cheater but a fact !!)

The best way is first to try word mode, only if this doesn't work you
should try another mode.
@endnode
